        {
            "title": "歐股個別發展 德英股市微升 法股挫0.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市收市個別發展。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.05%，報616點，盤中最多曾漲0.51%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數收報24154點，升87點，升幅近0.4%。英國富時100指數報10589點，升30點，升幅近0.3%。法國CAC指數表現較弱，收報8262點，跌11點，跌幅0.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報48026點，跌0.27%或128點；西班牙IBEX 35指數收報18089點，跌0.53%或96點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國廉航易捷航空(EasyJet)股價暴跌5%，因燃油成本上升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15883483-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%80%8b%e5%88%a5%e7%99%bc%e5%b1%95-%e5%be%b7%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%87-%e6%b3%95%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%ab0-1",
