            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 17:24:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "荃灣樂悠居2房620萬元成交   持貨4個月升值13%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> 中原地產荃灣柏傲灣分行新近促成荃灣樂悠居中層5室成交，實用面積420平方呎，兩房間隔，叫價638萬元，減價18萬元，以620萬元易手，實用呎價14762元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主於2025年12月以550萬元買入，持貨約4個月，賬面獲利70萬元或12.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880336-%e8%8d%83%e7%81%a3%e6%a8%82%e6%82%a0%e5%b1%852%e6%88%bf620%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a84%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc13",
